\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIndia\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"shruti-shekar-editor-in-chief-3\"\u003eShruti Shekar, Editor-in-Chief\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"Cosori Air Fryer\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/J5DLWCcxWvgr5rzvCtjwkP.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption itemprop=\"caption description\"\u003e\u003cspan itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\"\u003e(Image credit: Cosori)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eI didn\u0026#39;t buy much this Prime Day as some of the things I was looking at weren\u0026#39;t on sale. However, we did need a new air fryer, our old one is a bit janky. We opted for this Cosori in white and I\u0026#39;m pretty excited about getting it. Getting an air fryer is actually incredibly great for your kitchen and you can make a lot of great meals. I think it looks especially clean and classy, too.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e* COSORI Pro Gen 2 Air Fryer\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=169923\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.com%2FCOSORI-Performance-Functions-Dishwasher-Safe-Detachable%2Fdp%2FB0BD4BYR11%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-20%26ascsubtag%3Dac-us-1211640417137785468-20\" data-url=\"https://www.amazon.com/COSORI-Performance-Functions-Dishwasher-Safe-Detachable/dp/B0BD4BYR11?th=1\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://target.georiot.com/Proxy.ashx?tsid=169923\u0026amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Famazon.com%2FCOSORI-Performance-Functions-Dishwasher-Safe-Detachable%2Fdp%2FB0BD4BYR11%3Fth%3D1%26tag%3Dhawk-future-20%26ascsubtag%3Dhawk-custom-tracking-20\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Amazon US\" data-merchant-id=\"1471\" data-merchant-url=\"amazon.com\" data-merchant-network=\"Amazon\"\u003e\u003cdel\u003e$119\u003c/del\u003e \u003cstrong\u003e$99 at Amazon\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe other thing I got wasn\u0026#39;t on sale, unfortunately. I have been wanting one of these SpinWave mops because I\u0026#39;ve heard some really good things. I\u0026#39;ve also heard the cordless version isn\u0026#39;t very good when it comes to battery life so I opted for the corded version even though it\u0026#39;s not on sale. Since Bissell sends a portion of every sale to its pet foundation it\u0026#39;s OK. I\u0026#39;ll support any com